  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial sample embeds a future-dated evidence timestamp (W-CON-03): one ValidationResult carries an evidenceTimestamp that is 47 minutes after the package signatureTimestamp, simulating a race-condition artifact that would be easy to overlook during review.",
